<dl id="n33160b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n33" href="#n33160b">N33 (VI.B.4)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n33all.htm#n33160b"> 160(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> bent ground / on back</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">dead bodies were laid <mark>on their backs</mark> in coffins, instead of being <mark>bent</mark> up and laid on their side <mark>on the ground</mark>. <small> E.A. Wallis Budge, <a name="BOD1" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#BOD1"><cite title="source">The Book of the Dead</cite></a>, 2nd ed. (1909) xxvi</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
